{
  "name": "Bard: Inspiration Support — Bardic Inspiration + Vicious Mockery + Healing Word + Font of Inspiration",
  "description": "A level 5 College of Lore Bard supports a Fighter and Rogue against an Orc Warchief and a Bandit. Tests (1) Bardic Inspiration as bonus action granting a d8 die to an ally (CHA mod = 4 uses), (2) Vicious Mockery cantrip applying disadvantage on Wis save DC 15, (3) ally attack consumes the BI die and adds it to damage, (4) Healing Word as leveled bonus action spell (2d4 + CHA), (5) Font of Inspiration: bardicInspiration pool fully refreshes on a short rest at L5. Per RAW D&D 5e 2024 — scenario is expected to FAIL on any step where a feature is missing (Vicious Mockery not in spell catalog, BI die transfer to ally not implemented). Do not weaken assertions.",
